{"tid":1128783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱先去廁所尿兜屙尿俾人打.......","createTime":"2019-04-28T05:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T15:38:42.000Z","uid":218575,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8a03121fdf2c583ada2f4af6212dfe11385cec48","tid":1128783,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:18:21.000Z","msg":"話說呢排天氣熱 <br />\n成日流汗 咁肥仔黎講我都算健康<br />\n夏天一日都會幾枝水補充水份<br />\n飲得多水自然多尿屙 <br />\n<br />\n啱啱要出元朗老鏈咁遠<br />\n係地鐵上已經一路好急<br />\n落車一出yoho mall 已經即刻搵廁所<br />\n幾個尿兜都俾人用咗 好彩仲有個位<br />\n一除褲準備屙個時 仆你個街<br />\n係開叉尿！！！！<br />\n成條尿射咗落隔離個金毛mk條褲到 <br />\n俾佢質咗我幾拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好痛呀個頭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffa2b71600ef75d10430618309e58e2ed2dbbd6","tid":1128783,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"邊個蝦我肥仔<br />\n我打柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41bd1fd1d0124994f5d0d75d3b61ce26ae5d6e20","tid":1128783,"uid":113373,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>最後呼籲<br />\n<br />\n撤回修訂《引渡條例》遊行<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年4月28日<br />\n時間：下午3:00集合，4:00起步<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 <br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3678d716f6efb60c0bc1416b7cd2158de7ffa95a","tid":1128783,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:04:44.000Z","msg":"你開呢個 post expect 乜野 ?<br />\n<br />\n一堆 Gay 回覆 ? 0 /10 ?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實做乜鳩姐你 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9fb3da4cd28d74ad221129d4e9b71e52b08605","tid":1128783,"uid":21857